"{\"uid\": \"en.vietnamplus.vn-paris-olympics-vietnamese-swimmer-badminton-player-to-compete-on-jul-29-post290952.vnp\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Vietnamese swimmer Nguyen Huy Hoang and badminton player Nguyen Thuy Linh will start competing at the Paris 2024 Olympics on July 29.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 26, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4780501197684864e-28, \"text\": \"Huy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris (VNA)- Vietnamese swimmer Nguyen Huy Hoang and badminton player Nguyen Thuy Linh will start competing at the Paris 2024 Olympics on July 29.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically, Hoang will compete in the men's 800m freestyle qualification round and Linh will play against Australian player Tiffany Ho in the women's singles qualification round.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.845164162028436, \"rank\": 0.18317439694830523, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_Ho\", \"score\": 0.9999991659400461, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tiffany Ho\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_Ho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_Ho\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 32nd Southeast Asian Games (SEA Games 32) last year, Hoang brought home three golds and one bronze.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While at the SEA Games 31, he took five golds and broke two SEA Games' records.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 18th Asian Games (ASIAD 18) in 2018, Hoang won a silver medal in the 1,500m freestyle event.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The same year, when attending the Youth Olympics in Argentina, he took a gold medal in the 800m freestyle category.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9999997777495329, \"rank\": 2.2225039169997838e-07, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoang's road to Paris was paved with both triumph and adversity.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 886, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.503435639466706e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At ASIAD 19 last year, he clinched a bronze medal in the men's 800m freestyle event, punching his ticket to the Olympics with a time of 7:51.44.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Paris Olympics, Hoang will compete in his two favourite events - the 1,500m freestyle and the 800m freestyle.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For his second time at the Olympics, the swimmer from Quang Binh province aims to surpass his own professional index to achieve the best results and seek opportunities to enter the finals.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qu\\u1ea3ng_B\\u00ecnh_province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Quang Binh province\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qu\\u1ea3ng_B\\u00ecnh_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qu\\u1ea3ng_B\\u00ecnh_province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Linh - the number one female player of Vietnam - is in Group K with No 11 Beiwen Zhang of the US and No 80 Tiffany Ho of Australia.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Africa_Cup_of_Nations_qualification\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4354414668468902e-21, \"text\": \"Group K\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Africa_Cup_of_Nations_qualification\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Africa_Cup_of_Nations_qualification\"}, {\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9577863047542187, \"rank\": 0.044074228671264155, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.538352907906664e-11, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The predictions are that Linh, world No 26, and Zhang will have meet almost no resistance winning over Ho.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8712678847532927e-58, \"text\": \"Ho\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Linh secured a 2-0 win over Ho at the Spain Masters in March.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8712678847532927e-58, \"text\": \"Ho\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The direct match between Linh and Zhang will decide the group winner.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Linh is 15 below Zhang in the world rankings, the Germany Open first runner-up is at the same level with her.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In their latest meet last year, Linh beat Zhang 2-1 at the Arctic Open's last 16 round in Finland.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.9999997291143157, \"rank\": 2.708789889035959e-07, \"text\": \"Finland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Linh's second straight Olympics.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo in 2021, her competition ended at the group round./.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2037, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9744162762932859, \"rank\": 0.026255428966383897, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vietnamese female boxer Ha Thi Linh advanced to the second qualification round of the U60kg category after a decisive win over Feofaaki Epenisa from Tonga late July 27 at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.677379916966577e-12, \"text\": \"Tonga\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vietnamese shooter Trinh Thu Vinh ranked fourth at the women's 10-metre air pistol finale on July 28, missing out on winning a medal at the Paris 2024 Olympic event.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7567815908731618e-35, \"text\": \"Vinh\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinh\"}, {\"begin\": 2434, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3754785133404784e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Vietnamese sports team heading to the Paris Olympics 2024 received a send-off ceremony in Hanoi on July 17, hosted by the Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\", \"score\": 0.9797016671836977, \"rank\": 0.02071889177676626, \"text\": \"Hanoi\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Vietnam Film Week in Laos runs from December 2 to 6, showcasing award-winning Vietnamese titles.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7077130914357866e-15, \"text\": \"Laos\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\"}, {\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the new agreement, the Ho Chi Minh Relic Site at the Presidential Palace and Saint Petersburg State University of Russia will cooperate in key areas including joint scientific events, student internships, collection of materials related to Ho Chi Minh and bilateral relations, expert exchanges, and co-publishing new works on the President and the history of ties between Vietnam and Russia.\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 3128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\", \"score\": 0.9999997407676683, \"rank\": 2.5923244892763736e-07, \"text\": \"Ho Chi Minh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\"}, {\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 3121, \"end\": 3127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4978790525313254e-13, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"December's centerpiece is a showcase of Co Tu heritage from the central city of Da Nang, featuring immersive cultural experiences.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3210, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Da_Nang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.731821706063058e-30, \"text\": \"Da Nang\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Da_Nang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Da_Nang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Co Tu village space, artisans will stage the Pro ngooch brotherhood ritual, a centuries-old ceremony for settling disputes and reinforcing inter-village solidarity, alongside ceremonial toasts, folk singing, and festive displays of folklore and performing arts.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Acecook Vietnam's decision to elevate and extend its sponsorship package until 2030 sends a strong signal for the future of Vietnamese football, reflecting the company's sense of responsibility and long-term commitment to the sport.\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3539, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 3655, \"end\": 3665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the two-day \\\"Salon de l'Asie 2025\\\", visitors to the space were treated to four art performances each day, calligraphy demonstrations, martial arts displays and lively unicorn dances.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The month-long event served as a platform to amplify cultural exchange, art dialogue, and Hanoi's global visibility as a UNESCO Creative City.\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4046, \"end\": 4051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\", \"score\": 0.9797016671836977, \"rank\": 0.02071889177676626, \"text\": \"Hanoi\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hanoi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performance brought together 5,000 students performing in person at the Saigon Riverside Park in An Khanh ward, and another 55,000 students joining online from more than 150 schools across the city.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The artists also delivered performances celebrating the great friendship, special solidarity and comprehensive cooperation between the two nations.\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The blend of distinctive traditional art forms with modern creative elements created a rich and emotionally charged atmosphere which is imbued with cultural identity yet reflecting the spirit of a new era.\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The walking street aims to create a cultural and arts space at night to extend tourists' stay, improve local people's spiritual life, and contribute to the city's night-time economic development.\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the event, the ministry awarded certificates to the 50 selected masterpieces, including 14 literary works, 18 stage productions, 12 musical compositions, and six dance pieces, and launched the 2026-2030 campaign to inspire the next wave of Vietnamese literary and art creation.\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 5136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5099, \"end\": 5109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At SEA Games 33, Vietnam are placed in Group B alongside Malaysia and Laos.\", \"from\": 5138, \"to\": 5213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5155, \"end\": 5162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 5177, \"end\": 5184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.931317399652542e-22, \"text\": \"Group B\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 5195, \"end\": 5203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.618626908719322e-14, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}, {\"begin\": 5208, \"end\": 5212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7077130914357866e-15, \"text\": \"Laos\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the adjusted schedule, the team will open their campaign against Laos on December 3 before meeting Malaysia on December 11.\", \"from\": 5214, \"to\": 5343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5285, \"end\": 5289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7077130914357866e-15, \"text\": \"Laos\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\"}, {\"begin\": 5319, \"end\": 5327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.618626908719322e-14, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both matches will be played at Bangkok's Rajamangala Stadium.\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5375, \"end\": 5382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999999977444531, \"rank\": 2.222226237393642e-09, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At SEA Games 33, every Vietnamese athlete wearing the uniform will carry not only national pride but also the strong energy and support of millions of fans.\", \"from\": 5407, \"to\": 5563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5430, \"end\": 5440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the theme \\\"Cham Di San - Cam Chat Rieng\\\" (Touch the Heritage - Feel the Distinct Identity), the contest received 1,034 entries from 203 photographers nationwide, featuring diverse portrayals of tangible and intangible heritage, landscapes and cultural identity across all regions of Vietnam.\", \"from\": 5565, \"to\": 5862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5582, \"end\": 5586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chams\", \"score\": 0.9992704652631196, \"rank\": 0.0007300673459505752, \"text\": \"Cham\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chams\"}, {\"begin\": 5854, \"end\": 5861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Vietnamese community is an important part of Perth's multicultural fabric, contributing significantly to its economic, cultural and social life, said Perth Lord Mayor Bruce Reynolds.\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 6050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5868, \"end\": 5878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 5913, \"end\": 5918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.781092206040567e-16, \"text\": \"Perth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\"}, {\"begin\": 6018, \"end\": 6023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.781092206040567e-16, \"text\": \"Perth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\"}, {\"begin\": 6024, \"end\": 6034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\", \"score\": 0.9765497238201482, \"rank\": 0.02324821396129507, \"text\": \"Lord Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\"}, {\"begin\": 6024, \"end\": 6034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\", \"score\": 0.9765497238201482, \"rank\": 0.02324821396129507, \"text\": \"Lord Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_mayor\"}, {\"begin\": 6035, \"end\": 6049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Reynolds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bruce Reynolds\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Reynolds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Reynolds\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Vietnamese sports delegation, headed by Nguyen Hong Minh, Deputy Director of the Sports Authority of Vietnam, aims to win 91 to 110 gold medals at SEA Games 33.\", \"from\": 6052, \"to\": 6216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6056, \"end\": 6066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The PM urged every official, coach, and athlete to embrace their responsibilities, compete with total commitment, surpass personal limits, and treat each match as a final, while striving to set new personal bests and achieve regional records.\", \"from\": 6218, \"to\": 6460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event features works by 50 Vietnamese photographers and 14 international delegations with 36 members.\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6493, \"end\": 6503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each participating artist is showcasing three standout photographs.\", \"from\": 6568, \"to\": 6635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event serves as a cultural platform for Vietnam to showcase its revolutionary music achievements, alongside new compositions by Vietnamese musicians, to an international audience.\", \"from\": 6637, \"to\": 6820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6681, \"end\": 6688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.723831270719907e-23, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 6769, \"end\": 6779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also offers foreign artists an opportunity to gain deeper insight into the country, its people and its rich musical and cultural heritage, thereby strengthening friendships and enhancing the profile of Vietnamese professional music on the world stage.\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 7075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7026, \"end\": 7036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The display is organised into five sections covering his early organisational efforts, shared resolve in the fight against foreign invaders, mutual support and close ties, everlasting friendship, and an overview of Nguyen Ai Quoc - Ho Chi Minh's revolutionary work in China.\", \"from\": 7077, \"to\": 7351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7292, \"end\": 7306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nguyen Ai Quoc\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh\"}, {\"begin\": 7309, \"end\": 7320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\", \"score\": 0.9999997407676683, \"rank\": 2.5923244892763736e-07, \"text\": \"Ho Chi Minh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ho_Chi_Minh_City\"}, {\"begin\": 7345, \"end\": 7350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999989604476, \"rank\": 1.0394202523642745e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The exhibition features 140 artworks, with 70 by Vietnamese photographers and the remainder by Indonesian artists, showcasing vivid images of natural landscapes, traditional culture, customs, and everyday life in both countries.\", \"from\": 7353, \"to\": 7581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7402, \"end\": 7412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999757941224021, \"rank\": 2.4203774654652503e-05, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\",